{
  "text": "Curriculum units are found in Table 2 . In addition to basic education about the AF disease process and its impact on everyday life, curriculum units were included on AF self-management through lifestyle changes [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] 40 and on simple and sustainable changes that could be achieved for early success, including stress management.",
